{"tid":692031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[山雨欲來]唐英年倡香港資本市場用人民幣結算","createTime":"2018-06-06T09:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T09:28:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40c57c0d13b6bae4a424defd132be986d2b6cbdb","tid":692031,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:21:46.000Z","msg":"前政務司長、政協唐英年表示，本港資本市場可以鼓勵使用人民幣計價、結算等，助人民幣國際化。<br />\n<br />\n唐英年出席活動時表示，今年是本港發展離岸人民幣15年，隨着國家金融政策開放，人民幣國際化愈來愈快，境外人民幣市場逐步完善。而香港是境外第一及最大人民幣離岸中心，現時擁有6000億人民幣資金池，人民幣每日平均成交超過9000億元。<br />\n<br />\n唐英年認為，可利用粵港澳大灣區契機推動跨境人民幣，香港亦扮演「中國曼哈頓」角色，帶動大灣區發展。他又建議推動香港資本市場使用人民幣，鼓勵使用人民幣計價、結算等，助人民幣國際化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00001/1528188646064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00001%2F1528188646064&d=3SQJKRFdxrTWy%2FUlf%2FX81S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7db8015b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00001%2F1528188646064&h=12ca8c48\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00001/1528188646064</a>"},{"pid":"0ca4e8b2ba75a9edb924536fd26c4a59573f99f1","tid":692031,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:22:47.000Z","msg":"鬥快賣哂香港剩餘價值"},{"pid":"0ec1269a10f2288864945c27c14bf1076a6c3661","tid":692031,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"人民幣計價樓市又大升!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}